body:
This PR is a followup to #12581 and especially to @cvuosalo's comment (https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/12581#issuecomment-161434181). After #12581 the `logintpack` has different minimum by absolute value for positive and negative numbers. Here `PackedCandidateTrackValidator` is made aware of the different minima.

Tested in 800pre4, tiny changes expected under `Tracking/PackedCandidate` in `diffCov*Status` and `diffCov*UnderOverFlowSign` histograms for elements packed with `logintpack` (in practice should be visible in 1330.0 and 25202.0 workflows).

@rovere @VinInn
